subject: [junit] Enumeration of passed tests
msgSnippet: Hi: I need to get an Enumeration of all the tests that succeeded. I noticed that the TestResult class has methods for errors and failures --
messageBody:
Hi:

I need to get an Enumeration of all the tests that succeeded. I noticed that the TestResult class has methods for errors and failures --

java.util.Enumeration failures() Returns an Enumeration for the failures
java.util.Enumeration errors() Returns an Enumeration for the errors.

Is there a way I can get a list or vector or an enumeration of all the tests that succeeded in a Test Suite?

Thanks, Nishi.
